# 🐦 Flappy Bird - JavaScript Clone (Seahawks Edition)

Welcome to a personalized version of the classic Flappy Bird — rebuilt from scratch using HTML5 Canvas and JavaScript! Featuring a custom **Seattle Seahawks**-inspired look, this game is designed to be simple, responsive, and fun.

---

## 🎮 Gameplay

- Press **Spacebar** on desktop or **Tap** on mobile to make the bird flap.
- Avoid the top and bottom pipes.
- Score increases every time you successfully fly through a pipe pair.
- The game ends when the bird collides or falls below the screen.
- A "Game Over" screen shows your score and high score.

---

## 🧩 Features

✅ Smooth jump mechanics with gravity  
✅ Procedurally generated pipes every 1.5 seconds  
✅ High score tracking (per session)  
✅ Mobile/touchscreen compatibility  
✅ Game restart functionality  
✅ Pixelated graphics for a retro feel  
✅ Custom art for bird, pipes, and background  
✅ Seahawks theme & colors for that Seattle pride 🟦💚

---

## 🖼 Assets

All custom visual elements used in the game:

| File              | Description                |
|------------------|----------------------------|
| `flappybird.png` | The main bird sprite       |
| `toppipe.png`    | Top pipe image             |
| `bottompipe.png` | Bottom pipe image          |
| `flappybirdbg.png` | Game background image    |
| `index.html`     | Game logic & rendering     |

